    "description": "Miyamoto S是一款与微型板单一游戏的纸牌游戏。<br>这是一个日本风格的世界看法，羞耻出现在一个简单的艺术视觉中。<br>当你打开棋盘游戏盒时，它会跳到微型世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/8644b2554b893a69e5f4ae7123aad06a.poster.avif?t=1643535727\" width=636 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/8644b2554b893a69e5f4ae7123aad06a.webm?t=1643535727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/8644b2554b893a69e5f4ae7123aad06a.mp4?t=1643535727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>重要的策略是“当”，“在其中”，“播放”的地方。<br>每场战斗彼此捡起四张牌，并从建立甲板开始。<br>用各种技能收集主人并击败宫廷茶。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/df796f83db74a0a724af09dd6767420f.poster.avif?t=1643535727\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/df796f83db74a0a724af09dd6767420f.webm?t=1643535727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/df796f83db74a0a724af09dd6767420f.mp4?t=1643535727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/fe7df929b4a8c677e0878e3c1af3fa38.poster.avif?t=1643535727\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/fe7df929b4a8c677e0878e3c1af3fa38.webm?t=1643535727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/fe7df929b4a8c677e0878e3c1af3fa38.mp4?t=1643535727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Miyamoto S包括一封新卡片“柴犬”。<br>已添加包括柴犬在内的新单位。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/531f4db8ebf6b1a80b889edd85e7c4b5.poster.avif?t=1643535727\" width=700 height=384 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/531f4db8ebf6b1a80b889edd85e7c4b5.webm?t=1643535727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1768530/extras/531f4db8ebf6b1a80b889edd85e7c4b5.mp4?t=1643535727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
